{"tid":2366042,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"又想攞羅彩玲D相打J","createTime":"2021-01-14T08:12:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T09:49:07.000Z","uid":157640,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"777bb1276559215ec0095ea62d24cee76b9ab921","tid":2366042,"uid":157640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T08:12:07.000Z","msg":"TVB出爐視后蔡思貝在獲獎當晚，被台下的黑面「真視后」陳自瑤搶盡風頭，事隔數日，終於到蔡思貝「威一次」，事關《壹週刊》報道蔡思貝搭上周焯華（洗米華）拍檔Sam，年約30多歲的Sam是太陽金業集團老闆，去年中蔡思貝為其公司拍金飾廣告撻着，Sam發動瘋狂追求攻勢，又送名牌又管接管送，搵到筍盤的蔡思貝即飛起胡鴻鈞。不過，有讀者向《蘋果》爆料，Sam其實是有婦之夫，去年o靚模「嫩版朱茵」羅彩玲（Vivian）被爆包養生活富貴，原來男主角就是人夫Sam，有TVB姣精之稱的蔡思貝疑做三奶。"},{"pid":"502adfadeabd7a87b7c7f2e71f486d36399b6429","tid":2366042,"uid":119729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T08:15:27.000Z","msg":"羅凱鈴好J好多"},{"pid":"78ab01813228a0af2f7c0280f8455b46707ac325","tid":2366042,"uid":353587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"502adfadeabd7a87b7c7f2e71f486d36399b6429","tid":2366042,"uid":119729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T08:15:27.000Z","msg":"羅凱鈴好J好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T08:24:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0xMCLXO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0xMCLXO.gif&h=2b9ac33c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ae91478b84d9989fca8fd59a770af50c62e7c48","tid":2366042,"uid":157640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T09:47:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n61fx5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn61fx5b.jpg&h=917f9da4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n細細佬,正!!"},{"pid":"d3e95c15bfe7b6f682833e244e989dc0fedeed61","tid":2366042,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T09:49:07.000Z","msg":"椎名空<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}